#: src/faq.md:1
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "常見問題"

#: src/faq.md:3
msgid "Is this an official Rust project?"
msgstr "這是一個官方的 Rust 專案嗎？"

#: src/faq.md:5
msgid ""
"Yes. rustup is an official Rust project. It is the recommended way to "
"install Rust at https://www.rust-lang.org."
msgstr ""
"是的。 rustup 是一個官方的 Rust 專案。它是從 https://www.rust-lang.org 安裝 "
"Rust 的推薦方式。"

#: src/faq.md:8
msgid "How is this related to multirust?"
msgstr "這和 multirust 有什麼關係？"

#: src/faq.md:10
msgid ""
"rustup is the successor to [multirust](https://github.com/brson/multirust). "
"rustup began as multirust-rs, a rewrite of multirust from shell script to "
"Rust, by [Diggory Blake](https://github.com/Diggsey), and is now maintained "
"by The Rust Project."
msgstr ""
"rustup 是 [multirust](https://github.com/brson/multirust) 的繼任者 。 rustup "
"最初是 multirust-rs，由 [Diggory Blake](https://github.com/Diggsey) 將 "
"multirust 從外殼腳本重寫為 Rust 版本，現在由 Rust 專案維護。"

#: src/faq.md:17
msgid "Can rustup download the Rust source code?"
msgstr "rustup 可以下載 Rust 來源碼嗎？"

#: src/faq.md:19
msgid ""
"The source for Rust's standard library can be obtained by running `rustup "
"component add rust-src`. It will be downloaded to the `<toolchain root>/lib/"
"rustlib/src/rust` directory of the current toolchain."
msgstr ""
"可以透過執行 `rustup component add rust-src` 來取得 Rust 標準程式庫的來源碼。"
"它將被下載到當前工具鏈的 `<toolchain root>/lib/rustlib/src/rust` 目錄。"

#: src/faq.md:23
msgid ""
"The source for the compiler and tools must be obtained from the [Rust "
"repository](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/) or the standalone [source "
"tarballs](https://forge.rust-lang.org/infra/other-installation-methods."
"html#source-code)."
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.md:29
msgid "rustup fails with Windows error 32"
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.md:31
msgid ""
"If `rustup` fails with Windows error 32, it may be due to antivirus scanning "
"in the background. Disable antivirus scanner and try again."
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.md:34
msgid ""
"I get \"error: could not remove 'rustup-bin' file: 'C:\\Users\\USER\\\\."
"cargo\\bin\\rustup.exe'\""
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.md:36
msgid ""
"If `rustup` fails to self-update in this way it's usually because RLS is "
"running (your editor is open and running RLS). The solution is to stop RLS "
"(by closing your editor) and try again."
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.md:40
msgid "rustup exited successfully but I can't run `rustc --version`"
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.md:42
msgid ""
"Restart your shell. This will reload your `PATH` environment variable to "
"include Cargo's bin directory (`$CARGO_HOME/bin`)."
msgstr ""
